<li><b>Keep</b> The individuals included are defined by their combination of sex and sport. <a href="" title="User:Alansohn">Alansohn</a> (<a href="" title="User talk:Alansohn">talk</a>) 22:30, 14 April 2009 (UTC)</li></ul>
