<ul>
<li><b>Keep</b>: if a sport is <i>often</i> played in a gender-separated way, then having categories that reflect this is entirely appropriate, and it is not mixing two unrelated things. This category for korfball or showjumping may be debatable, but for most sports, it is a perfectly normal and natural categorization. <a href="" title="User:Fram">Fram</a> (<a href="" title="User talk:Fram">talk</a>) 09:30, 17 April 2009 (UTC)</li></ul>
